release.changelog:
Hello to the AI-powered Neptune Browser!
* You can now open the AI model as a separate tab from the top menu in the dropdown menu. You can change the model you want to use in the settings.
* The 'update available' error has been fixed on devices running Android 12 or earlier, even when weekly updates are made.
* We have reorganized the settings screen for easier access.
